FBIS4-16494 "drsov074_d_94017" FBIS-SOV-94-074 Daily Report 16 Apr 1994 Regional Affairs Yeltsin Appoints Representative for Chuvash Yeltsin Appoints Representative for Chuvash LD1604113694 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1046 GMT 16 Apr 94 LD1604113694 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS] [Text] Moscow April 16 TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin has appointed Mikhail Timofeyev presidential representative in the Republic of Chuvashia. A decree to this effect was signed on Friday.
